Hallogallo -- NEU! -- NEU!
I'm so Lonesome I Could Cry -- SQÜRL -- EP #2
Red Eyes And Tears -- Black Rebel Motorcycle Club -- B.R.M.C.
Red Mars I -- Loren Connors -- Red Mars
The Art of Fugue, BWV 1080: The Art of Fugue, BWV 1080: Contrapunctus 1 -- Johann Sebastian Bach, Fretwork -- J.S. Bach: The Art of Fugue, BWV 1080
